					</div>
					<div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm font-bold border border-white/5 bg-white/5 px-5 py-3 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm">
						<div class="flex -space-x-3">
							<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[#105971] bg-[#0a151b] overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center text-lg">🧔🏻</div>
